{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Horror Starter Pack</strong> includes all of the features of the base game <strong>PLUS 24 additional horror-themed assets</strong> perfect for creating a haunted mansion, mysterious graveyard, or a creepy crypt. <strong>The DLC pack represents a tremendous value compared to purchasing assets separately with in-app purchases</strong>. The pack includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>The base game for TTRPGs in 3D and AR and the Free Starter Set</strong> featuring digital dungeon and cavern terrain from Dwarven Forge and Fat Dragon Games, player minis from Hero Forge and Reaper Mini, plus our digital dice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>Wall, door, and window pieces</strong> to frame the old house on the hill above the graveyard, long since abandoned</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>Side, front, and corner roof pieces</strong> that try to hold back the rain that plagues the old mansion some say is haunted</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>1 x scrubby grass terrain tile</strong> (copy/paste to create a wasteland)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>4 x accessories</strong> for the old hearth: 3 portraits of a family long gone and a coat of arms</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>Graveyard gates and fencing</strong>, <strong>2 x headstones</strong> of the dearly beloved, a <strong>coffin</strong> ready to be interred, and a <strong>skeleton</strong> to hide inside!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>An ancient tree bereft of leaves</strong> that sways in the cold wind (set the amount of sway in Settings!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>All the NPCs for your nightmare adventure: Werewolf, Vampire, Ghost, Zombie and Skeleton</strong> (don\u2019t forget to copy/paste that Zombie to create a horde!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>3 x Ready-to-Play Maps</strong> using the above pieces\u2014perfect for when your party decides to tackle a bone chilling adventure on the darker side! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Lead the party in investigating an abandoned and dilapidated mansion, rumored to be haunted. Explore a graveyard showing signs of unnatural activity. Send the party down a path through a forest said to come alive at night. Or  combine them all into a master map for an epic adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use these maps to inspire your own maps that you can build and share with your TTRPG party for FREE or share with the community on the Mirrorscape HUB!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730222458","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284250/page.bg.jpg?t=1730222458","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284250/d0d277b7a858e919c707761671c0cac5e55da55e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730222458","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284250/d0d277b7a858e919c707761671c0cac5e55da55e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730222458","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},{"description":"In-App Purchases","id":35}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Horror Starter Pack</strong> includes all of the features of the base game <strong>PLUS 24 additional horror-themed assets</strong> perfect for creating a haunted mansion, mysterious graveyard, or a creepy crypt. <strong>The DLC pack represents a tremendous value compared to purchasing assets separately with in-app purchases</strong>. The pack includes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2022 <strong>The base game for TTRPGs in 3D and AR and 